Methods: The reason, why we create variables, the reason itself is your method
       : Methods are actions performed over variables

 accessModifier[public/private/protected] returnType[void/dataTypes] methodName(can/t parameters)
 {
    action over variables of the class;
 }

==========================================

1. Create an Employee Class
2. Create variables
   -fName;
   -lName;
   -basicSalary;
   -travelAllowance;

   -> PrintFullNameOfEmployee [fName + lName]
   -> CalculateSalary [basicSalary+ TravelAllowance]

